name: REBEL UNION
description: We're rebels tired of the broken financial system. As entrepreneurs, we've faced the wrath of web3 bullies and trad-fi frauds. We've felt your pain. But we won't surrender. We will fight like hell to bring order to the anarchy. Together, we've formed The Rebel Union, a force that will challenge the status quo. They hide in the shadows, while we remain unseen, yet ever-present, dismantling the corrupt system as we grow.
